<br>
Solo Exp<br>
1. Fire Blade (non opening blade)<br>
2. Tornado (parry opening CD)<br>
3. Blinding Rain (evade opening CD)<br>
4. Spectrum Blade (chains off Fire Blade)<br>
5. Meteor Shower (chains off Tornado)<br>
6. Blizzard (chains off Blinding Rain)<br>
7. Twin Star (chains off Meteor Shower)<br>
8. /stick<br>
<br>
Reasons:<br>
I used two very fast weapons, with this setup I can have three fingers on the 1,2,3 keys and just wait for the opener.<br>
I tried to do some research, and I don't think the defense penalty you get from fire blade makes you parry/evade less or git hit more often. If it does, it is not so much I could see it.<br>
<br>
Group Exp<br>
1. Taunting Blade (Taunt Blade)<br>
2. Snow Shower (Behind CD)<br>
3. Gale (chains off Snow Shower)<br>
4. Enervating Blade (Detaunt Blade)<br>
5. Tornado<br>
6. Blinding Rain<br>
7. /g Healer/Caster attacked<br>
8. /stick<br>
<br>
Solo RvR<br>
1. Fire Blade<br>
2. Spectrum Blade<br>
3. Tornado<br>
4. Flurry<br>
5. Triple Wield<br>
6. Sprint<br>
7. Face<br>
